data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER of a POOL HOME in the serene, mature, and friendly neighborhood of Reserve at Buckingham. With 4 bedrooms, Florida Room, formal dining area, 2 full bathrooms, and over 1800 sq ft, this home has plenty of space! Split floor plan and no carpet in this home! New LG appliances and Water Heater (2021), newer Pool Heater (2020), newer Roof (2018). Low HOA fees! At the gateway to Buckingham, nestled between Fort Myers and Alva, you'll find yourself minutes from Publix and Winn Dixie grocery stores, shopping, numerous restaurants, and Riverdale Public Library.
